York','Finger Lakes','Finger Lakes','Wagner','Grace House'),(229,4,9,85,14.00,'Treleaven 2006 Semi-Dry Riesling (Cayuga Lake)','A thoroughly honest effort, opening with lovely quince, apple and lemon fruit. The palate has a crisp lime edge and finishes with a kick of refreshing acidity. Drink now.','US','New York','Cayuga Lake','Finger Lakes','Treleaven','Semi-Dry'),(230,15,9,85,18.00,'Benessere 2005 Costa Del Sol Red (Napa Valley)','Not clear what the varietal blend is, but it\'s like a nice, easy southern Rhône wine. Soft and fruity, it\'s rich in jammy blackberry, cherry, Mandarin orange, chocolate and anise spice flavors.','US','California','Napa Valley','Napa','Benessere','Costa Del Sol'),(231,8,16,85,16.00,'Bloomer Creek 2006 Gewürztraminer (Finger Lakes)','Orange blossom and flowers lead on this Gewürtz, and on the palate, a citric, lemon edge outweighs the sweet and floral components that would give this wine a prettier edge. Nonetheless, the wine has an attractive, crisp and clean character and will pair well with grilled seafood and poultry.','US','New York','Finger Lakes','Finger Lakes','Bloomer Creek',NULL),(232,66,5,85,10.00,'Andean Sky 2007 Bonarda (Mendoza)','Meaty and rubbery, but that\'s young Bonarda. This is a sound wine with dark berry flavors, raisin and pulsing acidity. Still, there\'s modest roundness to the palate and length to the finish. Overall, it\'s tasty, full and borderline raisiny. Drink now.','Argentina','Mendoza Province','Mendoza',NULL,'Andean Sky',NULL),(233,67,9,85,12.00,'Angove\'s 2006 Red Belly Black Shiraz (South Australia)','Lifted cedar and pine notes interspersed with appealing woodsy scents give way to a surprisingly intense palate that shows some nice peppery notes but ultimately falls short on the finish. Nearly imperceptible tannins suggest early consumption.','Australia','South Australia','South Australia',NULL,'Angove\'s','Red Belly Black'),(234,5,3,85,28.00,'Silvan Ridge 2006 Reserve Pinot Noir (Willamette Valley)','